 our lives.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aDecision makingxPhysiological aspects. 0aNeurobiologyxPhysiological aspects. 0aNeuropsychologyxPhysiological aspects. 7aPSYCHOLOGY / Neuropsychology.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018 Englishz978311060420708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018z9783110603200oZDB-23-DPM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311063899840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300240917?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300240917423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300240917/original  a978-3-11-060420-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-063899-8  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPMb2018